metadata.name: Planet KOI-172.02
metadata.description:
According to Book of Dzyan, humanity in the 21st century is in the 5th sub-lineage of the 5th main lineage.

The year is 2301, 279 years later humanity has finished the 5th sub-lineage of the 5th main lineage and is now in the 6th lineage. Humanity spread across half the Milky Way galaxy and reached almost all habitable planets. However, after the galactic war in 2258, women in the Milky Way galaxy can no longer give birth naturally.

The civilization on planet KOI-172.02 managed succeed in altering the structure of the soil and they were able to inject last remaining embryos into the soil. After this stage humanity on the planet KOI comes to life from the soil.

Tynra is one of the woman scientists who is responsible from newborns on planet KOI. The needle device on her arm helps with feeding newborns during the birth process.
